msgid "gluon-config-mode:welcome"
msgstr ""
"Welcome to the setup wizard of your new Freifunk Aachen node. "
"Please fill out the following form and transmit it."

msgid "gluon-config-mode:pubkey"
msgstr ""
"<p>Please remember to move the network cable form the lan to the wan port, if your device has multible network ports.</p>"
"<p>This is your Freifunk node's public key, you do not need to do anything with it.</p>"
"<p>It is possible to use this key to place your node in the right network segment form its first connection, here are additional information:</p>"
"<p>The node's name (<em><%=pcdata(hostname)%></em>) and MAC (<em><%= sysconfig.primary_mac %></em>).</p>"
"<p>Your public Key: <em><%= pubkey %></em></p>"


msgid "gluon-config-mode:reboot"
msgstr ""
"<p>The node is currently rebooting and will try to connect to other nearby Freifunk nodes afterwards.</p>"
"<p>You can find lots of information on the Freifunk Aachen community on "
"<a href=\"https://freifunk-aachen.de\">our homepage</a>.</p>"
"<p>To get back to this configuration interface, press the reset button for "
"3 seconds during normal operation. The device will then reboot into config "
"mode.</p>"
"<p>Have fun with your node and exploring the Freifunk network!</p>"
